trans-unit.source: An airplane has two seats in the flight deck (for the pilot and co-pilot), and a number of rows of 1st class and 2nd class passenger seats. Each 1st class row contains four seats. Each 2nd class row contains five seats.
trans-unit.target: Un avion ha duo sedes in le cabina (pro le pilota e le copilota) e un numero de filas de sedes pro passageros del prime classe e del secunde classes. Cata fila del prime classe contine quatro sedes. Cata fila del secunde classe contine cinque sedes.

trans-unit.source: Build a formula (below) that calculates the total number of seats on the airplane as the rows are changed (above).
trans-unit.target: Construe un formula (ci infra) que calcula le numero total de sedes in le avion quando le numero de filas es cambiate (ci supra).

trans-unit.source: An airplane has two seats in the flight deck (for the pilot and co-pilot), and a number of rows of passenger seats. Each row contains four seats.
trans-unit.target: Un avion ha duo sedes in le cabina (pro le pilota e le copilota) e un numero de filas de sedes pro passageros. Cata fila contine quatro sedes.

trans-unit.source: An airplane has a number of rows of passenger seats. Each row contains four seats.
trans-unit.target: Un avion ha un numero de filas de sedes pro passageros. Cata fila contine quatro sedes.
